# Vapi Does Not Work on Localhost

The Vapi SDK (`@vapi-ai/web`) only works when the app is served from the production server URL. On `http://localhost:4321` (or any localhost port), Vapi returns a **403 "Key doesn't allow origin"** error and the call never connects — the microphone permission dialog will not appear.

**Do not debug Vapi mic/call issues on localhost.** Always test on the deployed server URL.
